27/08/2008
NICOSIA, Cyprus -- Advisers to the leaders of the two communities on the divided island are to meet on Wednesday (August 27th) to discuss remaining details ahead of direct talks on reunification. 
Greek Cypriot President Demetris Christofias and Turkish Cypriot leader Mehmet Ali Talat meet on September 3rd. 
(Phileleftheros- 27/08/08; Zaman - 26/08/08)
